{"tid":1962048,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來隻武漢肺炎病毒咁古惑，會出兩種抗體","createTime":"2020-04-07T08:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T09:47:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d688db9126a01d4688d9133943ee977f24c3ca","tid":1962048,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎爆發之後，不少國家實行隔離令，社會民生經濟活動大多停擺。停擺愈久，對各地傷害愈大，難道疫情一日未完，所有人都只能坐以待斃？歐洲多國現時正考慮抗疫的新對策 &mdash;&mdash; 以病毒抗體決定誰可以出門。首先進行大規模抗體測試，得到「免疫護照」（Immunity passports）的人即可回復正常生活。<strong><br />\n<br />\n意大利科學家指，新型冠狀病毒會產生兩類抗體，第一類通常在接觸該病毒後 5 到 6 天內出現，在 20 天後消失。而當病人康復時，該抗體會慢慢地被另一種抗體取代，只有檢測到第二種抗體時，才代表該患者可能已清除體內病毒。帕多瓦大學（University of Padua）微生物學教授 Andrea Crisanti 認為，這種抗體可能是決定誰可以安全退出隔離之列，重投工作的寶貴工具。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/04/07/immunity-passports/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F07%2Fimmunity-passports%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=fa09b8db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/04/07/immunity-passports/</a>"},{"pid":"52ec1638c9a99b7383df6b4c3f060e0feaf4b9fa","tid":1962048,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母支那生化武器"},{"pid":"a98474282a687e63df250354932160f83e25674d","tid":1962048,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"但第二隻抗體可以維持倒幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2e254555324cf7b0472bfdfdf5f7fd8ab8b0a3","tid":1962048,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"innate immunity vs acquired immunity?"},{"pid":"5215e174360e3f1b59dedd7adb186f776ed2daf9","tid":1962048,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"啫係點？本要開放兩種唔同疫苗？"}]}